{"tid":300352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東8毒販被判死刑，即時押到刑場處決","createTime":"2017-06-27T23:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T10:57:02.000Z","uid":30040,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5963c8d7057254776cd0bed062f90432952f9adc","tid":300352,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T23:16:23.000Z","msg":"上周六（24日），廣東陸豐、汕尾兩級法院，在陸豐市東海鎮人民體育廣場上，對18名涉及製毒、販毒及藏毒等罪行的罪犯公開宣判，其中13人被處死刑，8人隨後被押往刑場處決。<br />\n<br />\n從現場照片可見，大批民眾到場圍觀，也有毒販家屬聞判死刑泣不成聲。公開宣判的18名毒犯中，蔡X等8名來自陸豐「三甲」地區，因走私、製毒、販毒、藏毒等罪名被判處死刑立即執行，蔡X等5人被判處死刑緩期2年執行，李X等5名毒犯被判處有期徒刑10個月至15年不等。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498568671_9a49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498568671_9a49.jpg&h=d7bc2d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498568670_420b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498568670_420b.jpg&h=c63d3ac0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498568669_883b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498568669_883b.jpg&h=f812ef95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無知一問，點解呢個下半身要打格仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498568668_9fba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498568668_9fba.jpg&h=a8710dfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498568666_770e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498568666_770e.jpg&h=8ed9a037&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35f86d4b37eb0e6a6c2cf472c0b742ba2014f93e","tid":300352,"uid":8048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T23:18:36.000Z","msg":"公安都打埋格喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .."},{"pid":"3cd8b7f59a222c23e7567b92f7b70079f428cefb","tid":300352,"uid":1672,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T23:34:05.000Z","msg":"啲公安戴乜撚野黑超呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2592dd08365b7aca2635938b2bfe73a111f3ffe4","tid":300352,"uid":30040,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T23:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲公安戴乜撚野黑超呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚家屬認到樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1971b2b6f5550e8e20e39398bb8526c4a7d06dc3","tid":300352,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T23:42:23.000Z","msg":"如果個三個港人運到廣州先比人捉<br />\n<br />\n家下應該火化了"},{"pid":"92e3c12eb217e3917c4ca6a88c3c2c5429b023c0","tid":300352,"uid":35519,"like":103,"dislike":0,"score":103,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:47:38.000Z","msg":"「小趙，有8個領導要器官，安排一下。」"},{"pid":"2d7472c9bee08d6e01b7583cbec62d3acf9d7be2","tid":300352,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:48:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「小趙，有8個領導要器官，安排一下。」</blockquote><br />\n都要你販毒先得嫁"},{"pid":"13211e9c6532aa5d1692e5cc8e83bccae304155b","tid":300352,"uid":54359,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>「小趙，有8個領導要器官，安排一下。」</blockquote><br />\n都要你有[販毒]先得嫁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7921fdc4f31b02b573aee03e6